HEADWORD: Unaccountable
<hw>Un`ac*count"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not accountable or responsible; free from control.</def>  <rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not to be accounted for; inexplicable; not consonant with reason or rule; strange; mysterious.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un`ac*count"a*ble*ness</wf>}, <pos>n.</pos> -- <wf>Un`ac*count"a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- p. 1565 pr=PI -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unaccurate</ent>⟦br⟧
